  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d87\u0db3 \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca SJB \u0dc0\u0dd8\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd3\u0dba \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A SJB trade union leader who took the President's flag on a bed sheet was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chief Inspector Ajith Pedurarachchi, Station Commander of Vella Vrisi Police, said that Kaluthantrige Udeni Jayaratne, the trade union leader of Samagi Jana Balavega, was arrested today (29th) for illegally entering the presidential palace and using the official presidential flag on a bed sheet.",
        "The suspect was arrested after surrendering to the police through a lawyer. He is fifty-four years old and a resident of Malambe.",
        "The suspect is to be produced before the court. Investigations are being conducted on the instructions of Chief Inspector Ajith Pedurarachchi, Station Commander of Vella Vrisi Police."
      ],
